{"tid":1638073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[國際文宣方向整合] 今日香港 明日世界","createTime":"2019-10-08T07:48:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T01:40:36.000Z","uid":4308,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a9f8efb9df484216f9f3dcd4d3ba1808452344e","tid":1638073,"uid":4308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:48:06.000Z","msg":"呢幾日發生咁多外國商家佬為奶共跪低嘅事，唔係唔煲大佢吓?<br />\n1. Vans<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jWhjefE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjWhjefE.jpg&h=9a42ff9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國街頭服飾品牌Vans舉辦的鞋款設計比賽中，有一件加拿大設計師的參賽作品因為加入&ldquo;反送中&rdquo;元素，獲得許多香港網友支持。不過近日有網友發現，該款作品已遭官方刪除。Vans下午在官方臉書表示，從來沒有任何政治立場，但指有少部份作品因不符合比賽參與守則而被移除。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20191005-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%A3%93%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bvans%E9%9E%8B%E6%88%96%E5%B1%88%E6%9C%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%A2%E7%A2%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20191005-%25E5%258F%258D%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25AB%2598%25E5%25A3%2593%25E6%2595%258F%25E6%2584%259F-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258Bvans%25E9%259E%258B%25E6%2588%2596%25E5%25B1%2588%25E6%259C%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2595%25A2%25E7%25A2%25B0&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=c2af7d54\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20191005-%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%AB%98%E5%A3%93%E6%95%8F%E6%84%9F-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8Bvans%E9%9E%8B%E6%88%96%E5%B1%88%E6%9C%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%95%A2%E7%A2%B0</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aefimagesnew/aef_image/vqns.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faefimagesnew%2Faef_image%2Fvqns.jpg&h=01daf1ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好忘記vans係官網&quot;澄清&quot;之後再DQ左兩款鞋款都係關於反送中運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x2VS9qjr5Wk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx2VS9qjr5Wk&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=86a56ae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x2VS9qjr5Wk</a><br />\n蘋果搵一搵，發現不得含有政治元素呢條rule只有係香港區出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 火箭<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/309/5d9ac525ccfa1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F309%2F5d9ac525ccfa1.png&h=8c2cc72e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />火箭件事大家都知詳細，美國國內都痴左線咁不滿，火箭點比支那人封殺大家有目共睹不過想提一位勇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wUoKDDe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwUoKDDe.jpg&h=ed321fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KdsSNwU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKdsSNwU.jpg&h=2e8a4480&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為火箭呢件事燒國旗比人拉左<br />\n勇者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.  奶共暴雪<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.league-funny.com/imgur/15705144011_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.league-funny.com%2Fimgur%2F15705144011_o.jpg&h=6d685fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n暴雪奶共就人人都知，都估唔到食相咁撚衰<br />\n今（8）日判決正式出爐:<br />\nBlitzchung 將即刻起自大師職業賽除名，並取消其於第二賽季所獲之獎金。此外，自2019年10月5日至2020年10月5日止，此12個月期間內，Blitzchung將不具參與《爐石戰記》相關電競賽事之資格。即刻起，我們也將中止與兩位賽評的合作。<br />\n你話聰哥違規，條氣都唔撚順，我想問屌你老母果兩個賽評又關佢撚事?<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.league-funny.com/hs/article-128209?fbclid=IwAR3a4os6mHTAl75SnroRYO4MlzzR3wEeCIRWkHFkZ56_ShltO4sgRZ_TFok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.league-funny.com%2Fhs%2Farticle-128209%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3a4os6mHTAl75SnroRYO4MlzzR3wEeCIRWkHFkZ56_ShltO4sgRZ_TFok&d=NaStGCRJdOSKaO4BfYueNmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=3f7bddaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.league-funny.com/hs/article-128209?fbclid=IwAR3a4os6mHTAl75SnroRYO4MlzzR3wEeCIRWkHFkZ56_ShltO4sgRZ_TFok</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />小弟英文差唔識搞，希望各位文宣組幫幫手整<br />\n<br />\n或者其他英文好嘅都可以自己整投犒去TG英文文宣channel<br />\n附帶教學 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />:<br />\n【教學】自己文宣自己整，自己香港自己救：唔駛Ps/Ai，免費整圖app Canva<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1365992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1365992</a>"},{"pid":"19efb63d4962b8738c16a5692d61d83fc4dcb398","tid":1638073,"uid":69585,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:52:25.000Z","msg":"Howard<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e04cabf2714ba899da7e8ea2f68d8d277acb20c","tid":1638073,"uid":150267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"如果覺得資訊有亂混 入去睇下<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">所有行動 文宣post 轉曬去活動台</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1638034\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1638034</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"d8b8541a4848b862c74345761c74b6d962d0fe3c","tid":1638073,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:40:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">朋友send過黎,人地發緊功,我地都要對準</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.quora.com/What-are-some-c